{"tid":1029932,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"如何對付快線撚","createTime":"2019-02-20T14:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T18:28:54.000Z","uid":32247,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6564dac7f1ec141bcc03e50bdc8d5026d9da982c","tid":1029932,"uid":32247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:55:00.000Z","msg":"香港人已經愈來愈唔識得揸車，特別係去到星期六，日。吐露港條慢線直頭行得快過快線。行得貼又話人推，唔貼佢又拉龍。<br />\n<br />\n大家到底點對付快線撚？"},{"pid":"97bb83557a3de681a233b369091896624923c712","tid":1029932,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"推鳩佢"},{"pid":"cfa087537b1c533b16ed8c6362614ab30834383f","tid":1029932,"uid":32247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97bb83557a3de681a233b369091896624923c712","tid":1029932,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"推鳩佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:57:57.000Z","msg":"一架半架就話，有時前面都想快，俾一㗎頂住拉住4,5㗎龍，推都無用。而且真係次次咁順利咩？推人始終有風險<br />\n<br />\n有諗過響安，但係香港實在無呢種文化，你BO佢佢都未必意識到。一到weekend 頭都痛埋"},{"pid":"49d488816d7fcb622e67eda93998f15ebf415b50","tid":1029932,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:58:43.000Z","msg":"搭巴士叫司機行快線"},{"pid":"881cfa4a5a74e6797bbf3d1f4df6658ddbb7c9d1","tid":1029932,"uid":16061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:00:42.000Z","msg":"閃佢幾下會讓"},{"pid":"07781e50319b12386fc7dd6a2848fdba9ed1c902","tid":1029932,"uid":32247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49d488816d7fcb622e67eda93998f15ebf415b50","tid":1029932,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:58:43.000Z","msg":"搭巴士叫司機行快線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:01:16.000Z","msg":"分分鐘快過快線班LUN樣"},{"pid":"f0ded7ad5964030e40ca53244ce4de7b37d7ff9e","tid":1029932,"uid":32247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"881cfa4a5a74e6797bbf3d1f4df6658ddbb7c9d1","tid":1029932,"uid":16061,"like":5,"dislike