s/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:32:21.000Z","msg":"最好仲要有個男乘客坐前面<br />\n<br />\n車尾有無字都無所謂，啲快線L邊有可能睇到你尾"},{"pid":"a0121ec2b8df85c6cf010086e935eae08ce3e4b4","tid":1029932,"uid":32247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba4604dcbfbd204e57376bb217a7354aa252b909","tid":1029932,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0ded7ad5964030e40ca53244ce4de7b37d7ff9e","tid":1029932,"uid":32247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"881cfa4a5a74e6797bbf3d1f4df6658ddbb7c9d1","tid":1029932,"uid":16061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:00:42.000Z","msg":"閃佢幾下會讓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:02:22.000Z","msg":"問題係，你 前車 前車 前車(慢)<br />\n呢啲情況你閃都無用,係4，5㗎前車拉龍，佢理得你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:05:11.000Z","msg":"唔小心hi到honk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"如果多人咁做無所謂呀，問題係我揸咁耐車真係未聽過，見過有人響，最盡都係閃燈但前車一般好少理"},{"pid":"4eb58ee64249f7ccdb4a68be112effd9add94bdb","tid":1029932,"uid":30006,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:42:17.000Z","msg":"假日識行一定行慢線，快到仆街"},{"pid":"c20dfcaa6868620c49abba8373dd4b55dd6048f8","tid":1029932,"uid":32247,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4eb58ee64249f7ccdb4a68be112effd9add94bdb","tid":1029932,"uid":30006,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:42:17.000Z","msg":"假日識行一定行慢線，快到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:47:27.000Z","msg":"條氣唔順真係重點,<br />\n第一 <br />\n本身法例係要求從右線超車<br />\n<br />\n第二 <br />\n助長快線L，覺得行死快線無問題，左右線有位你唔走係你ON9<br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n你行慢線其實影響其他大車，例如貨車，巴士"},{"pid":"4dc91a011753b41c0dd42387f57f56856040764d","tid":1029932,"uid":68346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T16:13:24.000Z","msg":"乜都無撚用，太多發自內心既快線撚，小路入公路，係屎唔屎都要cut 出快線既人多到佔勁大部份<br />\n<br />\n差佬一日唔嚴厲執法，就唔會解決到呢樣野。調番轉，慈母高調捉一鑊金，應該last 到好耐"},{"pid":"343b5b0461ab7